social_posts.post_text: Feeling all the festive vibes! 🎄✨ Presenting my NEW Elf costume inspired by stilt walkers around the world. Had a blast at the #holidaysatthefarm event this weekend, and huge THANKS to @funtimeentertainment! Sharon, you’re an absolute gem and truly appreciated for making the season extra magical! 🌟 #ElfAdventures

🎄Holiday at the Farm! I had an amazing time at this event. Let me tell you… The volunteers working this event were super sweet, caring, and helpful! Especially Brittany who walked around with me the entire time! She was also my camera lady too 😉😌 I love having a handler! It makes gigs more fun! 
Also, Shoutout to Dallas County Fire Rescue & Police! 🫶🏽 You guys are awesome!!
